rComments: Great Professor. Gives proper instructions for assignments and dynamic lectures.

Great lecture content and flexible. Funny accent. However, he has a bit of punctuation and lack of clarity problems. Overall, a great prof who tries his best to convey as much knowledge and experiences to you. Very approachable and inspirational.

He gives you a clear goal and things to do. He will guide you through the process patiently and what he wants if you don't understand. It is not a 100% all the time confused studio with him, and you learn new stuff with him.
